data.description: NEW ROOF 2023! Beautiful 4/2 Single Family Home with space for the whole family and a large fenced in yard. Located in the sought-after Whitemarsh Community, a perfect location just minutes from the highway to get you wherever you want to be. This 2,372 square foot home has carpeted living room, formal dining room with chair rail and tray ceiling. Large kitchen has stainless steel appliances, new dishwasher and in-sink disposal, pantry closet, breakfast bar, plenty of counter space and cabinets. Adjacent to the kitchen is a tiled dining nook and carpeted family room. This split plan home has 2 carpeted bedrooms and 1 with wood look laminate flooring. All have walk-in closets and share a bath with shower tub combo. The carpeted Master Bedroom has a tray ceiling, seating area, access to the lanai through sliding glass doors, a large walk-in closet and ensuite bath. This large ensuite bath has a separate shower and soaking garden bath, 2 sinks and vanity table along with a separate water closet. Additional features of this home are: ceiling fans with light kits throughout, crown molding in the public areas and master bedroom, interior laundry room, screened and covered lanai leading to backyard. There is even room for a pool! This could be your forever home! Be sure to watch the video of this home and schedule your appointment to see it today!
